  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore an abandoned hotel and search for clues while trying not to succumb to your fears in this ode to 90’s survival horror games. You will solve puzzles, face off against supernatural entities, and use limited resources to maintain your sanity so you can explore deeper in The Pines Hotel and find out what really happened to Emi Kosuke. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Cinematic Survival Horror gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Possibly the scariest and most disturbing game ever created</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Heart-rending Detective Noir Story, guaranteed to traumatize you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Eerie Original Soundtrack written and performed by the solo developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Perma-death (for the protagonist and possibly you, too)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Loosens your grip on reality and also your bowels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Tutorials and menus intentionally deceive you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-May summon the recently deceased into your gaming room</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/498fb8d8666d5b0ea5644769f8f8822c.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/498fb8d8666d5b0ea5644769f8f8822c.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/498fb8d8666d5b0ea5644769f8f8822c.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/493d76d6106c432dd3a167b379865245.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/493d76d6106c432dd3a167b379865245.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/493d76d6106c432dd3a167b379865245.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/6557841ea804f46888e28bd3a7ce4284.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/6557841ea804f46888e28bd3a7ce4284.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/6557841ea804f46888e28bd3a7ce4284.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cf0eeaeddbab18ead19a8587c1e559e1.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Explore an abandoned hotel and search for clues while trying not to succumb to your fears in this ode to 90’s survival horror games. You will solve puzzles, face off against supernatural entities, and use limited resources to maintain your sanity so you can explore deeper in The Pines Hotel and find out what really happened to Emi Kosuke. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/b16252cde7e285fd8ccd55b5935edd9a.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Cinematic Survival Horror gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Possibly the scariest and most disturbing game ever created</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Heart-rending Detective Noir Story, guaranteed to traumatize you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Eerie Original Soundtrack written and performed by the solo developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Perma-death (for the protagonist and possibly you, too)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Loosens your grip on reality and also your bowels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Tutorials and menus intentionally deceive you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-May summon the recently deceased into your gaming room</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/66c5f0db40ad8ff741b38d8083fe21a0.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.poster.avif?t=1742495051\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.webm?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/cc9342fabf79a9c632ef1d647fd5cdac.mp4?t=1742495051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153190/extras/498fb8d8666d5b0ea5644769f8f8822c.poster.avif?t=174